
# Requirements

* Include setup instructions
* echo results of:
    1. most improved batting average if at-bats > 200 # For 2009 -> 2010
    2. OAK.players.map(&:2007).each(&:slugging_percentage)
    3. AL and NL Triple Crown Winners for 2011 and 2012 || "(No winner)"

# Formulas

* batting_average = hits / at_bats
* slugging_percentage = (hits - <non-hits> + (2*doubles) ...) / at_bats
* triple_crown_winner = (highest_batting_average && most_home_runs && most_rbi) && at_bats >= 400

